creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml:
It's finally here, everything you've been waiting for to help you get in the best shape of your life. From strength and endurance training to cardio, core and mobility, all the way around to corrective exercise for preventing injuries and rehabbing old ones. And yes of course our favorite, healthy food that's actually bomb!

With the Cole Brothers Fitness App, you can start tracking your workouts and meals, measuring results, and achieving your fitness goals, all with the help of your veteran master trainers. Download the app today! And be sure to check out our website at: colebrothersfitness.trainerize.com
descriptionShort: Start achieving your fitness goals with the help of veteran master trainers.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

As usual, we’ve also made some other back-end upgrades to make your experience even better.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
As much as we’d all like, big changes unfortunately don’t happen overnight. That’s why we’ve introduced habit coaching—a new way to help clients make small, sustainable lifestyle changes! Trainers can now create habits within our Master Habit Library and prescribe them to clients. As clients complete habits each day, they will earn habit streaks and unlock special achievement badges over time.
As always, we’ve also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
